{
  "stem": "1160.4",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they have outside houses, rows of outside houses.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You see, when we arrive to Gostling, when we were-- the door, on one side of the door, soldiers.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They were already captured soldiers.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I don't know, they were French, or I don't know, most probably.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They weren't Hungarian.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They were captured all ready.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And they were there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And they were, they were taken out from there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I don't know where they went.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And the Jews were put in there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "There were bunk beds, both side of the barrack, and long tables, not one, but was the length of the barrack.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But it was full.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "This barrack was full.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "This was full.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And when we arrived, and on the table, those soldiers-- because they left us some, like nothing, cookies, on the table, a pile of it.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I saw that right away.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I started-- but other children, because a lot of children were there-- they saw it.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I, I dashed to that table.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Right away I fell on it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I filled up my hands.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But I wasn't quick enough to straighten up and get up from there, so all the other children on me.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And the grownups also, some of them were there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And they were all trying to grab.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Because we were terrible hungry.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I couldn't move.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I was completely, like, nailed down there with bodies.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And the breathing was very hard, I remember.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I could hardly breath.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I was concentrating that my nose should get a little air.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So by the time everybody got off me-- and the hands, I could feel the hands.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Everybody was grabbing, grabbing, grabbing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You could feel nails.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I got up.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I ended up with crumbs in my both hands.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
